*galeon-1.3.2 (09 Mar 2003)

  09 Mar 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> galeon-1.3.2.ebuild:
  Version Bump. GTK2 Version of Galeon, needs Mozilla compiled with GTK2
  support.

*galeon-1.2.8 (19 Feb 2003)

  23 Feb 2003; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.8.ebuild :
  Change snapshot param to ./configure to set it to the current version
  of mozilla running.  The DEPEND *should* ensure that we have the correct
  version of mozilla installed, but this should also enable more experienced
  users to say build galeon against mozilla-1.3b without hacking this.

  19 Feb 2003; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.8.ebuild :
  Update version.

  04 Feb 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7-r1.ebuild :
  Mark stable on alpha

  08 Jan 2003; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7-r1.ebuild :
  Mark stable for x86.

  26 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild :
  Mark stable for x86.

*galeon-1.2.7-r1 (26 Dec 2002)

  26 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7-r1.ebuild :
  Add UTF8 support to the google smart bookmarks.  Note that
  it will probibly only work for a newly created bookmark ...

  24 Dec 2002; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild :
  Added ~ppc to keywords

  22 Dec 2002; foser <foser@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild galeon-1.2.6.ebuild :
  Added scrollkeeper dep (bug #12583)

  16 Dec 2002; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild :
  Add ~alpha to KEYWORDS

  04 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild :
  Fix to DEPEND on mozilla-1.2*.

*galeon-1.2.7 (01 Dec 2002)

  06 Dec 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild :
  I added the mozilla tree flag to configure to make it build with moz 1.2.1

  01 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.7.ebuild :
  Update version.  Closes bug #11376.

*galeon-1.2.6 (16 Sep 2002)

  20 Sep 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.6.ebuild :
  Added a patch to make it build with mozilla 1.0.1 and not 1.0.  Also changed 
  the dependencies for this.

  
  16 Sep 2002; Bruce A. Locke <blocke@shivan.org> galeon-1.2.6.ebuild:
  Version bump, recommended gcc 3.2 ./configure fix, and unneeded patch
  removal.  Note: This does not fix the upstream bug involving crashes
  with forms and gcc 3.2.  (see GNOME bugzilla bug #67691)

*galeon-1.2.5-r1 (29 Aug 2002)
  06 Sep 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.5-r1.ebuild :
  fix for  http://bugs.gentoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=6866 again
  
  31 Aug 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.5-r1.ebuild :
  added a patch for scrollkeeper omf fixed against DTD.
  not worthy of updating the revision IMO. 

  29 Aug 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.5-r1.ebuild :
  Fix for the crash on close bugs 
  thanks to TGL <degrenier@easyconnect.fr> for the fix


  
  25 Jul 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.5.ebuild :
  some minor dep changes to make it not pull in gnome2 stuff while we wait for the new portage syntax
  
  14 Jul 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> galeon-1.2.5.ebuild :
  Add an check for Mozilla compiled against gtk+-1.2, if not quit with
  an error message.

  14 Jul 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :
  Add SLOT, FEATURES, and LICENSE entries.

