  26 May 2002; Ryan Phillips <rphillips@gentoo.org>

  New release

*galeon-1.2.2 (23 May 2002)

  26 May 2002; Ryan Phillips <rphillips@gentoo.org>

  Unmasked 1.2.2

  22 May 2002; Ryan Phillips <rphillips@gentoo.org>

  Added shell for 1.2.2.  The gcc 3/3.1 patches do not apply
  to this source base.  I don't have the newer versions of GCC installed
  yet, and have masked this release until a stable version is verified.

